  <entry>
    <title>payload-dumper-go提取boot</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/11/12/payload-dumper-go%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96boot/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/11/12/payload-dumper-go%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96boot/</id>
    <published>2022-11-12T09:51:15.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-03-25T04:21:41.648Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1、下载手机系统包：<a href="https://xiaomirom.com/">XiaomiROM</a>（一定要下载和手机系统版本一致的系统包）</p><p>2、下载 <strong>payload-dumper-go</strong>：<a href="https://mrzzoxo.lanzoui.com/b02plgdpi">lanzoui.com&#x2F;b02plgdpi</a>（解压出来）</p><p>3、解压系统包（只需要payload.bin文件）</p><span id="more"></span><p>4、复制 <strong>payload.bin</strong> 文件到 <strong>payload-dumper-go</strong> 文件夹里面</p><p><img src="https://cdn.magiskcn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/2efa273a75fd6b7.jpg" alt="payload-dumper-go提取boot（payload提取boot.img）插图"></p><p>5、打开CMD命令行</p><p><img src="https://cdn.magiskcn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/35beee9e1b2e940.jpg" alt="payload-dumper-go提取boot（payload提取boot.img）插图1"></p><p>6、按照提示输入 b</p><p><img src="https://cdn.magiskcn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/1bc49334127f327.jpg" alt="payload-dumper-go提取boot（payload提取boot.img）插图2"></p><p>7、提取成功</p><p><img src="https://cdn.magiskcn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/9f415bbcdc6445c.jpg" alt="payload-dumper-go提取boot（payload提取boot.img）插图3"></p><p>8、打开 <strong>img</strong> 文件夹 就可以看到提取的 <strong>boot.img</strong> 了</p><p><img src="https://cdn.magiskcn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/c3362e52caa3aab.jpg" alt="payload-dumper-go提取boot（payload提取boot.img）插图4"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;1、下载手机系统包：&lt;a href=&quot;https://xiaomirom.com/&quot;&gt;XiaomiROM&lt;/a&gt;（一定要下载和手机系统版本一致的系统包）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、下载 &lt;strong&gt;payload-dumper-go&lt;/strong&gt;：&lt;a href=&quot;https://mrzzoxo.lanzoui.com/b02plgdpi&quot;&gt;lanzoui.com&amp;#x2F;b02plgdpi&lt;/a&gt;（解压出来）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、解压系统包（只需要payload.bin文件）&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
